messages.messageBody:
Dear All,

Zane is a very well known provider of educationl content. They just launched a new site and making it available for free for the first 30 days. You have to register to access the content:

www.zaneeducation.com

There might be some interesting information in the content and since it is free, why not take advantage of it?

Please feel free to pass this along to other groups.

Kind regards,
Anna
